window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This audiobook, <i>Parts Work</i>, describes our inner psychological world in ways that are moving, thought-provoking, sometimes humorous and often poignant. The audiobook shows how we can disentangle ourselves from the problematic habitual patterns in which we get stuck, and offers ways of positively using our particular talents and style for a fuller life. Through practical examples, the audiobook helps us to understand ourselves and others better.</p> <p>Sharon Eckstein's illustrations are not included in this audio edition. <i>Parts Work</i> is wonderfully narrated by Scott R. Pollak.</p>"; 
